org.pikater.shared.database.jpa

Class JPAExperiment

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPAAbstractEntity
      • org.pikater.shared.database.jpa.JPAExperiment

  • @Entity
public class JPAExperiment
extends JPAAbstractEntity
    Class JPAExperiment represents record about the experiment, that is part of a batch.

    This class also contains a list of results, that were created by the certain experiment.
